2019 like other years wasn’t short of scandals – from politics to the religious sector. Allelua Ministries International is one of the faith organisations whose credibility has come under scrutiny. From a purported resurrection to fresh allegations questioning the discredited ministry, claims of actors faking illnesses and disability were detailed in SABC’s Cutting Edge story, which raked over a million views on YouTube. Our reporter Maageketla Mohlabe takes us back. Watch report below: 